\">廣播道要人！！</span></span><br />\n港台俾人圍緊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/684540395290425/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F684540395290425%2F&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=b3bc6632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/684540395290425/</a><br />\n<br />\n8.24 2pm藍絲包圍港台行動：<br />\n<br />\n如果藍絲得十幾隻，唔使理<br />\n但如果多過100 人：<br />\n邊個藍絲搞搞震，就即刻反包圍攬炒<br />\n<br />\n同藍絲混亂 &gt;<br />\n塞廣播道\t&gt;<br />\n廣播道豪宅出催淚彈 &gt;<br />\n亂埋出聯合道 &gt;<br />\n推幾個藍絲入軍營 &gt;<br />\n雜物同催淚彈跌入軍營 (閘門好矮)&gt;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍走出黎，攬炒成功</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(浸大對面個門口無乜設防)<br />\n係真正攬埋藍絲入去炒，到時其他市民都無得淨入義士數<br />\n<br />\n希望浸大同樂富巴絲留意住，<br />\n有需要就出動反包圍<br />\n但敬請保持自身安全"},{"pid":"951778502ca96c50da8faaa487015fe82d3fcd31","tid":1500803,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"802ce674366e7eec2a395ed1c5b60cbcf1c359bb","tid":1500803,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6182b67a57de2c3f12aa8bc260c8ed986fc1913e","tid":1500803,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84841f615ffebec6038003c32989591cf195ebb7","tid":1500803,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be0b1ae94b591d1469d27c02bef69b6abe88188","tid":1500803,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92a51c484d622d55b8ef9ad5ccc2f14ab6839af2","tid":1500803,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT